## 사용 예제

### 예제 1: 패스워드 해싱

```freelang
fn hash_password(password: string) -> string {
    SHA256::hash(password).to_hex()
}

fn verify_password(password: string, hash: string) -> bool {
    hash_password(password) == hash
}
```

### 예제 2: 메시지 인증

```freelang
let key = "shared_secret"
let message = "important data"

// 생성
let signature = HMAC::sha256(key, message).to_hex()

// 검증
let expected = HMAC::sha256(key, message).to_hex()
let valid = signature == expected
```

### 예제 3: 데이터 암호화

```freelang
fn encrypt_data(plaintext: string, key: string) -> string {
    AES256::new(key).encrypt(plaintext)
}

fn decrypt_data(ciphertext: string, key: string) -> Result<string, string> {
    AES256::new(key).decrypt(ciphertext)
}
```

